data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This beautiful one-level home features 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The floor plan provides a seamless flow between the living room and kitchen areas. The bedrooms have ample space for relaxation and privacy. The backyard is perfect for family gatherings, barbecues or even just a simple peaceful evening. This house is located near shopping centers, schools and even the interstate. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your 'HOME SWEET HOME"!!!
